node.text: Every 3 seconds a girl under the age of 18 is married. That’s 12 million girls a year robbed of their futures, put at risk of violence, ill health, and trapped in poverty. Join me in helping to end the international child bride crisis. Head to vowforgirls.org for more info ! @vowforgirls

node.text: March is Women's Month, and I'm so proud to join these strong women ( @sleepinthegardn & @theparisberelc ) and @childrescuecoalition to speak up for children who are being sexually abused across the globe. If you can, please donate to help CRC rescue even more children, and let's turn their whispers into roars. #jointhefight Link in bio 🙏🏼

feeling so grateful for a wrap on Ragdoll and for all the beautiful friends & memories I made 🙏🏼
Cannot wait for you all to see this coming to your 📺’s soon ! Thank you to so many people but especially @matineeidle , Thalissa, the genius Freddy Syborn, everyone at Sid Gentle… too many to name but wow we did it. Congrats everyone !

•Written & directed by: @jesseharris

• Produced by : @dtucci27 - @tiziano.tucci - @greglauritano - @nancy_cartwright - @moni_g_r_ - @jesseharris 
• Executive producer: me 😱
• Cinematographer : @oztavio 
• Editor: Luis Carballar
• Music by: @thenewtonbroth3rs 
• Color by: @josephbicknell - @company_3 
• Production designer : @carlos_iribarne 
• Production companies: @tucciandcompany - @spottedcowent - @blackmagic.film - @abcdepictures - @vagabondproductionservices 

And countless other amazing people that helped to make this all possible. Forever grateful to all of you!
